}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "AP699E9NL"<......>" and "REV"<..>"1.0" kind of looks like it's silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. .. but the photo quality is terrible.
Default settings are per the FCC manual + sample label. :The OUI used (08:86:3B) is per the sample label. The SSID format would seem to be '''belkin.XXX''', but the pattern of the last 3 characters is not known.
===Probable included PSU(s)=== The power supply shown in the FCC photos is a '''[[SGE|Shenzhen Gongjin Electronics]]''' S05A12-120A050-P4.
